    <briefdescription>
<para>Complete patient record including demographics and vital sign history. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The readings array acts as a sequential log: index 0 holds the first reading, index reading_count-1 holds the most recent. The record is considered full when reading_count == MAX_READINGS.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>No dynamic memory is used. All storage is stack/static allocated. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
